      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Overview",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If your app intents or app entities expose variables with predefined values, support the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppEnum"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "protocol in those types. When an intent parameter or entity property conforms to this protocol,"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the system can suggest values readily in conversations. For example, consider a food",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "ordering app that offers small, medium, and large beverages, and defines an intent that takes the"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "beverage size as a parameter. If the person doesn’t specify a size when placing an order, but the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "parameter’s type supports the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppEnum"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol, the system can prompt for one of the defined"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "sizes automatically. If you can represent each value of an enumeration as a URL, also"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "add support for the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/URLRepresentableEnum",
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
